card.rules: Madness 1UR Whenever you draw a card, you may discard a card. Until end of turn, you may cast an instant or sorcery from your graveyard until end of turn. Then exile it. T: Draw a card.

card.name: Nom Anor, Galactic Saboteur
card.rules: T: Commit a treachery and then search your library for a land and put it onto the battlefield tapped. Whenever you commit a treachery, return target creature to an owner’s hand. Nom Anor, Galactic Saboteur becomes a copy of it until end of turn, except it has this ability.

card.name: Orbital Bombardment
card.rules: Splice onto Artifact UB (As you cast an Artifact spell, you may reveal this card from your hand and pay its splice cost. If you do, add this card’s effects to that spell.) Orbital Bombardment deals 2 damage to each non-Officer creature.

card.name: Ord Mantell, Republic Outpost
card.rules: Ord Mantell enters the battlefield tapped unless you attacked with a Rebel creature this turn.

card.name: Ossus, Academy’s Home
card.rules: Ossus, Academy’s Home enters the battlefield tapped unless there is a Jedi instant or sorcery in your graveyard.

card.name: Painful Interrogation
card.rules: Splice onto artifact 1U/B Target player discards a card from their hand at random. If it was a land, create a Holocron.

card.name: Peace Negotiations
card.rules: (As this Saga enters and after your draw step, add a lore counter. Sacrifice after III.)

card.name: Rakatan Empire
card.rules: Madness 2BR (If you discard this card, discard it into exile. When you do, cast it for its madness cost or put it into your graveyard.) Whenever you commit a treachery, you may create a 1/1 red Rakatan creature token with menace.

card.name: Rebel Shotcaller
card.rules: RR: Return target blocked creature you control to its owner’s hand. WW: Untap target creature.

card.name: Regal Warrior
card.rules: As long as Regal Warrior’s power is less than one, it has double strike.

card.name: Roaring Defender
card.rules: Convoke, Protector Tap four creatures: Draw a card.

card.name: Saber Throw
card.rules: As an additional cost to cast this spell, you may sacrifice an artifact. Saber Throw deals 5 damage to target creature or player.

card.name: Secret Intelligence
card.rules: Whenever you splice onto an artifact, you may activate an ability of Secret Intelligence. W: Gain three life. U: Draw a card. B: Create a Holocron.

card.name: Seek the Past
card.rules: When seek the Past enters the battlefield, exile a Jedi instant or sorcery from your graveyard with converted mana cost three or less. When another Jedi enters the battlefield, you may cast a copy of the exiled card without paying its mana cost.

card.name: The Senate
card.rules: T: Tap target creature or artifact. That target’s controller creates a Holocron artifact. Sacrifice 3 Holocrons: Destroy The Senate. Any player may activate this ability.

card.name: Shedao Shai, Overlord
card.rules: Protection from artifacts (This creature can’t be blocked, targeted, dealt damage, or enchanted by anything artifact.) Whenever Shedao Shai attacks, it gets +1/+0 for each land under your control until end of turn. 1RG: Search your library for a land card and put it onto the battlefield tapped. Then, if you control six or more lands, create a 1/1 red Yuuzhan Vong Warrior creature token with protection from artifacts.

card.name: Sith Ghostcaller
card.rules: Whenever you cast a Sith spell, put a +1/+1 counter on Sith Ghostcaller. When Sith Ghostcaller dies, create X 1/1 red Sith creature tokens, where X is Sith Ghostaller’s power.

card.name: Sith Succeeder
card.rules: Deathtouch Whenever Sith Succeeder attacks, you may commit a treachery. If you do, Sith Succeeder deals X damage to target player, where X is the number of creatures in your graveyard.

card.name: Stalwart Defender
card.rules: Convoke, Protector T: Target creature deals damage equal to its toughness until end of turn. Whenever you gain life, put a +1/+1 counter on Stalwart Defender.

card.name: Starkiller
card.rules: As long as Starkiller is attacking, it gets +5/+0 until end of turn. As long as Starkiller is blocking, it gets +0/+5 until end of turn.

card.name: Tactical Operation
card.rules: Splice onto Artifact 1W Gain X life, draw X cards, and each opponent discards a card. If you spliced onto artifact, gain 2 life instead.
card.flavor: “Their military abilities are undeniable, but their chances for long-term stability are nonexistent.”

card.name: Talzin, Shaman
card.rules: When Talzin, Shaman enters the battlefield, search your library for a creature and put it into the graveyard. T: Commit a treachery. At the beginning of your end step, if there are five or more creatures in your graveyard, transform Talzin.

card.name: Trade Secrets
card.rules: At the beginning of your upkeep, reveal the top card of your library. If it is a non-creature spell, put a bounty counter on target creature. Whenever a bounty is resolved, return a creature from your graveyard to your hand.

card.name: Vergere the Questioning
card.rules: Cumulative Upkeep: Deal 1 damage to target creature you control. Whenever a creature you control that could transform would die to Vergere’s cumulative upkeep, transform it instead.
card.flavor: “Is it what the teacher teaches or what the student learns?”

card.name: Vong Shaper
card.rules: Beasts you control have evolve. T: Target Beast gets +X/+0 until end of turn, where X is the highest power among Beasts you control.

card.name: Vote of No Confidence
card.rules: Target player returns a creature they control to its owner’s hand. If the creature isn’t legendary, you may put a legendary creature in your hand onto the battlefield.

card.name: War for the Capital
card.rules: Untap all lands you control. They gain “T: Target creature you control fights another target creature.” until end of turn.

card.name: Warrior for the Freed
card.rules: Whenever Warrior for the Freed becomes untapped, scry 1. R, T: Deal 1 damage to target creature. W, Q: Gain 1 life.

card.name: Yavin IV Temple
card.rules: Yavin IV Temple enters the battlefield tapped unless you gained life this turn.

card.name: Youngling Mentor
card.rules: Vigilance T: Until end of turn, creatures you control deal damage equal to their toughness. 4GW: Create a 0/2 white Jedi Knight creature token.

card.name: Alliance Spymaster
card.rules: Skulk (This creature can’t be blocked by creatures with greater power.) Whenever a legendary creature enters the battlefield or attacks, scry 1.

card.name: A’Sharad Hett, Raider
card.rules: Landfall - Whenever a land enters the battlefield under your control, A’Sharad Hett, Raider fights another target creature. At the beginning of your end step, if you control seven or more lands, transform A’Sharad Hett.

card.name: C-3P0, Human-Cyborg Relations
card.rules: 1W/U: Return C-3P0, Human-Cyborg Relations to its owner’s hand. Create a Holocron. Whenever you splice onto an artifact, you may transform C—3P0, Human-Cyborg Relations.

card.name: Cartel Contractor
card.rules: Bounty Whenever a creature with a bounty counter your opponent controls dies, you may put a bounty on target creature an opponent controls.

card.name: Dark Apprenticeship
card.rules: Madness 1B/RB/R Enchant creature with converted mana cost four or less. Gain control of enchanted creature. When enchanted creature dies, commit a treachery and return enchanted creature to the battlefield under its owner’s control.

card.name: Duel of the Fates
card.rules: If you control more Sith, creatures you control get +2/+0. If you control more Jedi, creatures you control get +0/+2. If you control an equal number of Sith and Jedi, creatures you control get -1/-1.

card.name: Entechment
card.rules: Enchant a creature you control. Enchanted creature cannot attack or block. When enchanted creature dies, return it to the battlefield with and gain 2 life. It becomes an artifact in addition to its other types.

card.name: Focus the Will
card.rules: As an additional cost to cast this spell, pay 4 life. Prevent all combat damage that would be dealt until your next turn.

card.name: Hateful Witch
card.rules: T: Deal 1 damage to each player. T, Commit a treachery: Instants and sorceries cost 2 less to cast until end of turn.

card.name: Hatred of Machines
card.rules: Creatures you control have haste. 2R/G: Create a 1/1 red Yuuzhan Vong creature token. Activate this ability only if your opponent controls an artifact.

card.name: Last Resort
card.rules: Target creature you control gets +3/+0 until end of turn. Sacrifice it at the end of the turn.

card.name: Malgus, Front Line Tactican
card.rules: Madness 1U/B (If you discard this card, discard it into exile. When you do, cast it for its madness cost or put it into your graveyard.) Whenever Malgus, Front Line Tactician would be sacrificed, you may transform it instead.

card.name: Nashtah, Padawan
card.rules: At the beginning of your end step, if two creatures you control died this turn, transform Nashtah, Padawan.

card.name: Shaak Ti, Clone General
card.rules: Vigilance T: Add W or G. T: Target creature deals combat damage equal to its toughness until end of turn. At the beginning of your upkeep, if you control a creature with toughness 4 or more, transform Shaak Ti, Clone General.

card.name: Unyielding Order
card.rules: Creatures you control get +0/+1. 3GW: Creatures you control deal damage equal to their toughness until end of turn.

card.name: A280 Blaster Rifle
card.rules: Equip 2 Equipped creature gains “T: Target creature deals 2 damage to target player.”

card.name: AT-AT
card.rules: Crew 2 Trample At the beginning of your end step, if AT-AT was blocked this turn, sacrifice it.

card.name: Bacta Tank
card.rules: When Bacta Tank enters the battlefield, put 3 bacta counters on it. At the beginning of your end step, remove a bacta counter from it and return a non-artifact creature you own that died this turn to your hand.
card.flavor: “Some pretty serious burns, but nothing a night in the bacta tank won’t fix.”

card.name: Bountyhunter Bowcaster
card.rules: Bounty Equip 2 Whenever equipped creature destroys a creature with a bounty counter on it, put a bounty counter on another target creature.

card.name: Carbonite Block
card.rules: Bounty When Carbonite Block enters the battlefield, exile target non-land permanent with a bounty counter on it until Carbonite Block leaves the battlefield. Put a bounty counter on it.
card.flavor: “Yes, he’s alive... and in perfect hibernation.” - Darth Vader

card.name: Darksaber
card.rules: Equip 1 Equipped creature gets +1/+1 and gains lifelink and deathtouch. When equipped creature dies, an opponent gains control of Darksaber.
card.flavor: “I claim this sword, and my rightful place as leader of Death Watch!” - Darth Maul

card.name: Hailfire Droid
card.rules: Crew 3 (Tap any number of creatures you control with total power 3 or greater: This Vehicle becomes an artifact creature until end of turn.) Hailfire Droid gets +1/+1 for each other artifact you control.

card.name: Holoprojector
card.rules: Whenever you cast a spell, exile it. You may cast the most recent spell that was exiled by Holoprojector, except it costs 2 more to cast.

card.name: Jedi Holocron
card.rules: Sacrifice Jedi Holocron: Add one mana of any color. 1, T: Add W, G, or U.

card.name: Rebellion Y-Wing
card.rules: Flying, Crew 3 Rebellion Y-Wing cannot be blocked by creatures with less power than it.

card.name: Sith Holocron
card.rules: Sacrifice Sith Holocron: Add one mana of any color. 1, T: Add R, B, or U.

card.name: Stormtrooper Armor
card.rules: Equip 1 Equipped creature gets +1/+1. Whenever you sacrifice equipped creature, you may attach Stormtrooper Armor to another creature you control.
card.flavor: Great aim.

card.name: Drommund Kaas, Sith Capital
card.rules: Drommund Kaas enters the battlefield tapped unless you committed a treachery this turn.

card.name: Jedi Temple
card.rules: T: Add C. T: Add U, G, or W. Activate this ability only to cast or activate a Jedi spell.

card.name: Nal Hutta, Glorious Jewel
card.rules: Nal Hutta, Glorious Jewel enters the battlefield tapped unless a creature has a bounty counter on it.

card.name: Sith Temple
card.rules: T: Add C. T: Add U, R, or B. Activate this ability only to cast or activate a Sith spell.
